me ideas\nabout why boosting works that may be misconceived, and in some recommendations\nthat may be misguided. [arXiv:0804.2752]\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Apr 2008 10:20:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-12-18"}
