e deSitter expanding state\n(deS$_{+}$), the state H=0 or $H=+\\infty$ state. In the case of the negative\ncosmological constant we obtain the past and future asymptotic states as the\nEinstein static universes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Apr 2008 11:42:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 26 Apr 2008 11:32:02 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 4 May 2009 17:23:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-18"}
